{"tid":1776954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"收購倫交所失敗被批蛇吞象  李小加：港交所才是象","createTime":"2019-12-10T01:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T02:56:52.000Z","uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"50bea6ada9e6874808d835b81008df1dd3f3c141","tid":1776954,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"港交所(00388)行政總裁李小加出席香港經濟峰會2020致辭時表示，無論香港人對社會運動立場如何，相信大家會堅守本港的核心價值，最終一定會走過艱難。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，對於港交所早前宣布收購倫敦證券交易所被批評是蛇吞象，李小加認為，港交所才是象，</span>並指未來會繼續進行收購，但需要配合天時地利人和。<br />\n<br />\n李小加提到，本港要自行發展固定收益及大宗商品十分困難，日後有機會會以收購來發展相關業務。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"691bda3fc0a58d0708228e36b8ba1cc1ba8d98e4","tid":1776954,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"癌症擴散"},{"pid":"382a4997bb33c0c3ace5ba755f475fa73b650842","tid":1776954,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:39:00.000Z","msg":"（Twitter戰線）歐盟Magnitsky Act有重要進程<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776924</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">twitter要人: 歐盟今日一致通過啟動Magnitsky Act 立法程序，詳細仲要傾，但歐洲戰線開啟左啦，快啲入去講邊個國家的人最需要被裁裁啦！！</span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n幫手入去retweet同推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5821583a396de392e63429cda65b0e68a13510e1","tid":1776954,"uid":21002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"小粉紅 :我們什麼都是最好的"},{"pid":"9c1798fa782eb83393fb9f60a1a30d00bd02f43e","tid":17769